---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ContactForm from "../components/ContactForm.astro";
---

<Layout title="Agora | Reclaiming the Commons" description="A distributed community focused on mutual support and physical presence.">
  
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-6 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8 relative z-10">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-widest text-white">
        AGORA
      </h1>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-zinc-400 font-serif italic max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Building the infrastructure for a life lived <span class="text-white">offline.</span>
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 pt-4">
        <a href="/organization" class="bg-white text-black px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-zinc-200 transition">Join a Chapter</a>
        <a href="/philosophy" class="border border-zinc-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-white/10 transition">The Manifesto</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-white/[0.02] rounded-full blur-3xl -z-0"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-zinc-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16 text-center md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Reclaim our community, together</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl text-lg">
          Agora is not a service you subscribe to; it is a movement you sustain. We don't provide "content"—we provide the framework for mutual support and collective action.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950 border border-white/5 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Collective Stewardship</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Members work together to secure and maintain physical spaces—halls, gardens, and workshops—that exist outside the reach of neoliberal real estate markets.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950 border border-white/5 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"></path><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Organic Co-Creation</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Events aren't ”curated” for you. Local chapters use our Social Network to pool skills and labor, turning every gathering into a collaborative act of community building.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-950 border border-white/5 space-y-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.42 4.58a5.4 5.4 0 0 0-7.65 0l-.77.78-.77-.78a5.4 5.4 0 0 0-7.65 0C1.46 6.7 1.33 10.28 4 13l8 8 8-8c2.67-2.72 2.54-6.3.42-8.42z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Mutual Solidarity</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Your Sponsor and Chapter are your safety net. We replace corporate insurance and transactional services with real-world human accountability and aid.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="class="py-32 px-6 text-center border-t border-zinc-800">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">The Agora is waiting.</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">
        Stop scrolling. Start building. Join a local chapter today and help us reclaim the commons.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-4">
        <ContactForm />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>